<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">6倍速算法，由于6=5+1，所以某数乘以6，只要将某数折半，扩大10倍再加上某数，便是其积。其口诀是：六分一五两步算，原数上面加折半。可用公式</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">a×6=a÷2×10+a</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">136×6=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 136×6</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=136÷2×10+136</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=68×10+136</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=680+136</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=816</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>